    ],
    "answer": null,
    "explanation": "<p>According to the question,</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1lu3rj278/267d4077-c57c-4802-a502-b7135870406d/1dd58a40-e8e6-11ee-a641-edca611b2ae2/file-1lu3rj279.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1lu3rj278/267d4077-c57c-4802-a502-b7135870406d/1dd58a40-e8e6-11ee-a641-edca611b2ae2/file-1lu3rj279.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"VITEEE 2022 Aptitude - Coding and Decoding Question 3 English Explanation\"></p>\n<p>$$\\begin{aligned}\nA O &amp; =B C=3 k m \\\\\\\\\nO D &amp; =C D-C O=10-6 \\quad(\\because C O=B A) \\\\\\\\\n&amp; =4 ~\\mathrm{k m}\n\\end{aligned}$$</p>\n<p>$$\\therefore$$ Shortest distance,</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{aligned}\nA D &amp; =\\sqrt{A O^2+O D^2} \\\\\\\\\n&amp; =\\sqrt{3^2+4^2}=\\sqrt{9+16}=\\sqrt{25} \\\\\\\\\n&amp; =5 \\mathrm{~km}\n\\end{aligned}$$</p>",
